description:
This is a 30 minute workout called '30 Minute HIIT Cardio Indoor Cycling Workout | Lose Weight Fast' from the channel GCN Training.
The workout falls under Cardio/Indoor biking and Cardio/HIIT.
It's suitable for Intermediate and Advanced fitness levels.
You'll need Exercise Bike for this workout.
The workout has a The Firestarter and The Meditative Grind vibe.
The technique difficulty is Beginner.
The effort required is Challenging.

Original workout description: Welcome to the first ever indoor HIIT cycling session with GCN Training! This is a tough but short session which is perfect for anyone tight on time, or looking to get a great session done in just half an hour.
